}

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>AI Readiness Services</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">For businesses that want professional help implementing AI Readiness improvements. All services are based on your specific audit results and needs.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-2 mb-4">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Schema Implementation</h2>
        <p>We implement the structured data your website needs:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Organization / LocalBusiness schema</li>
          <li>Service and Product schema</li>
          <li>FAQPage schema</li>
          <li>OfferCatalog for service grouping</li>
          <li>knowsAbout expertise signals</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Includes validation, testing, and documentation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Full AI Readiness Package</h2>
        <p>Complete optimization for AI discoverability:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All schema implementation</li>
          <li>Content restructuring for AI extraction</li>
          <li>FAQ content creation with schema</li>
          <li>Technical SEO fixes</li>
          <li>GEO optimization</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Comprehensive service for maximum AI visibility.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Run the free audit</strong> - See exactly what your site needs</li>
        <li><strong>Review your report</strong> - Understand the findings and recommendations</li>
        <li><strong>Contact us</strong> - Discuss which improvements matter most for your business</li>
        <li><strong>Get a quote</strong> - We provide specific pricing based on your needs</li>
        <li><strong>We implement</strong> - Professional implementation with testing and validation</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4" style="background: var(--bg-alt);">
      <h2>Pricing Approach</h2>
      <p>We quote based on your specific situation because every website is different. Factors include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Number of pages requiring schema</li>
        <li>Complexity of your services/products</li>
        <li>Current technical state</li>
        <li>Content restructuring needs</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Run the free audit first, then contact us for a specific quote based on your results.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <p>Not sure what you need? Start with the free audit.</p>
      <a href="/audit/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Run Free Audit</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
